        <abstract>
            <p>TMR believes rate of limestone formation is same now as in past.</p> 
<p>He expects his address [of 10 Oct 1876] on geological time [<hi rend="italic">Proc. Liverpool Geol. Soc.</hi> 3 (1878): 211–35], which contradicts William Thomson’s view of the earth’s age, to appear soon.</p> 
